{"tid":770728,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比利時中場韋素降薪加盟多蒙特","createTime":"2018-08-07T10:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T17:29:29.000Z","uid":163248,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4e418ab756b34641a2a1893c6adc845af67aa3d2","tid":770728,"uid":163248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"德甲勁旅多蒙特以2000萬歐元從中超的天津權健簽入比利時中場韋素（Axel Witsel）。據報，韋素大幅降薪，他在中超年薪1800萬歐元，但在多蒙特的實際年薪只得750萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n29歲的韋素昨日（8月6日）抵達瑞士，與在該地集訓的多蒙特大軍會合。多蒙特為原本效力天津權健的比利時中場韋素支付2000萬歐元（約1.8億港元）的解約金，令權健放人。儘管權健不滿，因為中超轉會窗已關，但根據國際足協規例，只要德國轉會窗未關，多蒙特就可以簽人。<br />\n<br />\n韋素參與多蒙特操練（按圖放大）<br />\n<br />\n世界盃後就決定離開中超<br />\n<br />\n今夏以主力身分為比利時贏得世界盃季軍的韋素說：「世界盃後，我的目標就是要由中國重返歐洲。我很高興也很自豪，能夠為多蒙特比賽，當我們首次見面後，不用多考慮就答應。多蒙特是歐洲其中一間最好的球會，我急不及在8.1萬名球迷面前上陣。」<br />\n<br />\n韋素除了接受多蒙特官網訪問外，還在個人社交網站留言，多謝中國球迷的支持，「經過18個月在中國的日子後，我想多謝天津權健的每個人，給予我一段奇妙的經歷。我們一起創下了很多難忘的時刻。多謝球迷、職員及球隊，我們一起的時光是畢生難忘的。」他去年協助權健贏得中超季軍，獲得亞冠盃資格。<br />\n<br />\n中超年薪達1800萬歐<br />\n<br />\n此外，德國《圖片報》披露了韋素的合約，他與多蒙特簽約4年，年薪750萬歐元，若包括獎金等，可達1000萬歐元，但他在權健的年薪就高達1800萬歐元。換言之，他今次是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">降薪140%</span></span>加盟多蒙特。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E5%BE%B7%E7%94%B2-%E6%AF%94%E5%88%A9%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%A0%B4%E9%9F%8B%E7%B4%A0%E9%99%8D%E8%96%AA%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E8%B6%85-%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E5%A4%9A%E8%92%99%E7%89%B9%E7%B0%BD%E7%B4%844%E5%B9%B4-045100904.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%2594%25B2-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259F%258B%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E9%2599%258D%25E8%2596%25AA%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E8%2592%2599%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E7%25B4%25844%25E5%25B9%25B4-045100904.html&d=CByY6opXVAj6kKRM0DXF1QEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=473d5a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E5%BE%B7%E7%94%B2-%E6%AF%94%E5%88%A9%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%A0%B4%E9%9F%8B%E7%B4%A0%E9%99%8D%E8%96%AA%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E8%B6%85-%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E5%A4%9A%E8%92%99%E7%89%B9%E7%B0%BD%E7%B4%844%E5%B9%B4-045100904.html</a><br />\n<br />\n想問問點計140%？<br />\n利申：唔識微積分"},{"pid":"6d38b864f7732ecb4ddaa4a4d08e8766ddc6a330","tid":770728,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"750 x (1+140%)"},{"pid":"43371ec73dad2c6589b43e80e6e64d9ca39a734e","tid":770728,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"1800/2.4"},{"pid":"7ee056d0f0fb75c2a6d599c3936a021b37ea4ef3","tid":770728,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"嗰份舊約可能係陰陽合同嚟..."},{"pid":"91a300317a20b7706eab6186d54d27ee16c0f4ac","tid":770728,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"倒貼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938a706961d9ff60e8cca8fc53bcaccf2c263258","tid":770728,"uid":163248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d38b864f7732ecb4ddaa4a4d08e8766ddc6a330","tid":770728,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"750 x (1+140%)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98970323506d2b65826e31202889e7442708eb83","tid":770728,"uid":163248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43371ec73dad2c6589b43e80e6e64d9ca39a734e","tid":770728,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"1800/2.4"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3829e8f7656951f712646c0b73498ea79d49c953","tid":770728,"uid"